1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:24,199
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, kroz ova tri dana smo imali priliku promišljati o svojem pozivu i evo i kroz sjajna predavanja, odnosno propovjedi koje imao velečasni Matej, mogli smo napraviti jedan zapravo ispit savjesti, ugledajući se, bilo kao očevi, bilo kao majke, bilo kao mladi, na uzor koji imamo u svetom Josipu.

2
00:00:24,199 --> 00:00:50,700
[SPEAKER_00] I jučer je velečasni Matej govorio o Josipu kao skrivenom kralju i baš većina nas, evo i kad smo se čuli prije ove duhovne obnove smo gledali, očemo se negdje poklopiti, ali baš kao da je duh sveti sve slagao, smo se sjajno tu zapravo nadopunili, većina nas će na skriven način živjeti tu svoju kraljevsku ulogu, a to što joj živimo na skriven način ne znači da se ona ne treba vidjeti.

3
00:00:50,700 --> 00:01:10,700
[SPEAKER_00] I tu se slažem baš sa velečasnim, ne volim kad se svetog Josipa prikazuje ko nekog šonjavca koji je eto bio tamo negdje povučen sa strane i ne vjerujem da je takav bio, zapravo i po mističnim viđenjima i svete Brigite i blažene Katarina Emerih se vidi da zapravo nije bio takav.

4
00:01:11,159 --> 00:01:23,280
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da bi mi to svoju kraljevsko dostojanstvo, kraljevsku čast i kraljevsku ulogu trebali živjeti tako da se ona vidi. Zašto? Zato jer ako se vidi onda ona i privlači, onda mi možemo biti svjetlo.

5
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:30,640
[SPEAKER_00] Ovdje katolika nema puno, kažu 10%, ali ja ćete kroz predavanje da je to dovoljno da zasvjetli.

6
00:01:30,640 --> 00:01:35,560
[SPEAKER_00] Jel mi smo pozvani biti sol zemlje? Jel se sol vidi u juhi?

7
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:39,579
[SPEAKER_00] Aj kuharici, kad kuhate juhu, jel se vidi sol poslije?

8
00:01:40,260 --> 00:01:44,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ali zamislite tu juhu bez soli, kakav je njen okus? Nikakav.

9
00:01:44,099 --> 00:01:48,280
[SPEAKER_00] Zato nas Bog i poziva. Isus često kaže ne boj se stado malo.

10
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:54,920
[SPEAKER_00] I uvijek su se velike stvari u povijesti događale od jednog malog stada koje se čvrsto oslonilo na gospodina.

11
00:01:54,920 --> 00:02:02,959
[SPEAKER_00] I zato smo pozvani otkrit iznova svoju kraljevsku ulogu i zaživjeti ono na što nas Bog poziva.

12
00:02:02,959 --> 00:02:09,939
[SPEAKER_00] Da vam malo pomognem da razumijete što to znači, ispričat ću vam jednu prispodobu.

13
00:02:09,939 --> 00:02:13,360
[SPEAKER_00] Jednu priču o orlu i kokoši.

14
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:20,620
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo je jednom jedan orao koji je pao iz gnjezda i slomio krilo.

15
00:02:20,620 --> 00:02:24,599
[SPEAKER_00] I čovjek koji je bio na paši sa ovcama ga je pronašao.

16
00:02:24,599 --> 00:02:26,219
[SPEAKER_00] I vidio je da mu je slomljeno krilo.

17
00:02:26,219 --> 00:02:29,620
[SPEAKER_00] I bilo mu je žao i poveo ga je kući.

18
00:02:29,620 --> 00:02:32,400
[SPEAKER_00] I stavio ga je među pilići.

19
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:35,120
[SPEAKER_00] Da odrasta među pilićima.

20
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:43,599
[SPEAKER_00] I taj orao je rasao, ali pošto je odrasao među pilićima, se počeo je ponašat kao pilić.

21
00:02:43,599 --> 00:02:47,139
[SPEAKER_00] Malo da nam dočaram kako je on živio.

22
00:02:47,139 --> 00:02:49,400
[SPEAKER_00] Možete ustati svi da se malo zagrijemo sad.

23
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:56,840
[SPEAKER_00] Znate da postoji ona izreka, ne znam da li kod vas kažu glupko kokoš.

24
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:58,400
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kažu to i kod vas.

25
00:02:58,400 --> 00:02:59,840
[SPEAKER_00] Glupa kokoš, jel?

26
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:02,139
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo vidjeti kako se taj orao ponašao.

27
00:03:02,460 --> 00:03:03,900
[SPEAKER_00] Kako kokoši zobe u kukuruz?

28
00:03:03,900 --> 00:03:04,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo malo.

29
00:03:04,500 --> 00:03:06,120
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde, ajde, slobodno.

30
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kako se osjećate sad, doktor Ajde?

31
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:11,639
[SPEAKER_00] Jesu još ćete malo glupo, jel da?

32
00:03:11,639 --> 00:03:18,039
[SPEAKER_00] I zapravo kad je došao taj čovjek koji ga je našao, je vidio je bilo mu žao.

33
00:03:18,039 --> 00:03:22,719
[SPEAKER_00] Vidio je šteta orla, predivan, krila su mu se razvila, perije.

34
00:03:22,719 --> 00:03:27,840
[SPEAKER_00] A on kljuca i zoba kukuruz, nabija se glavom dole.

35
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:33,580
[SPEAKER_00] I onda je našo jednog sokolara, znate, sokolara koji je trenirao sokole za let.

36
00:03:33,580 --> 00:03:37,659
[SPEAKER_00] I on je uzeo tog orla i počeo ga je voditi u planinu.

37
00:03:38,979 --> 00:03:42,919
[SPEAKER_00] I tu je ora otkrio svoj pravi poziv i počeo letiti.

38
00:03:42,919 --> 00:03:44,599
[SPEAKER_00] Nemojte, ne, ne, ne, ne, ostavite.

39
00:03:44,599 --> 00:03:49,099
[SPEAKER_00] I tu je ora počela, ajmo letiti sad ko orao.

40
00:03:49,099 --> 00:03:52,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde, ajde, ajde, zagrijedite se.

41
00:03:54,020 --> 00:03:56,300
[SPEAKER_00] Kraljevska čast znači biti slobodan od obzira.

42
00:03:56,300 --> 00:03:58,560
[SPEAKER_00] Jel se bolje osjećate tako?

43
00:03:58,560 --> 00:03:59,900
[SPEAKER_00] Jel vam ljepši?

44
00:03:59,900 --> 00:04:01,039
[SPEAKER_00] Možete sjediti sad.

45
00:04:01,039 --> 00:04:08,259
[SPEAKER_00] E, ono što je tužna istina iza ove šaljive priče,

46
00:04:08,259 --> 00:04:13,020
[SPEAKER_00] da velika većina kršćana zobaju kukuruzu.

47
00:04:13,020 --> 00:04:16,699
[SPEAKER_00] Nemaju pojma kosu i nemaju pojma što ima.

48
00:04:16,699 --> 00:04:20,699
[SPEAKER_00] Jer im je džavao uspio ukrast to kraljevsko dostojanstvo.

49
00:04:20,699 --> 00:04:22,920
[SPEAKER_00] Znate kad smo ga dobili?

50
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:26,079
[SPEAKER_00] Dobili smo ga na dan naše krštenja.

51
00:04:26,079 --> 00:04:32,939
[SPEAKER_00] I evo katekizam točka 1268 kaže ovako o našem pozivu.

52
00:04:32,939 --> 00:04:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Krštenici tako postaju živo kamenje

53
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:40,720
[SPEAKER_00] i ugrađuju se u duhovni dom za sveto svečenstvo.

54
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:44,920
[SPEAKER_00] Oni po krštenju imaju udjela u Kristovu svečenstvu,

55
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:48,300
[SPEAKER_00] u njegovom proročkom i kraljevskom poslanju.

56
00:04:48,300 --> 00:04:52,819
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su rod izabrani, kraljevsko svečenstvo,

57
00:04:52,939 --> 00:05:00,819
[SPEAKER_00] sveti puk, narod stečeni da navješta silna dijela onoga kojih iz tame pozva k svojem divnom svjetlu.

58
00:05:00,819 --> 00:05:02,879
[SPEAKER_00] Pogledajte te izraze.

59
00:05:02,879 --> 00:05:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Rod izabrani, kraljevsko svečenstvo, sveti puk,

60
00:05:08,620 --> 00:05:12,759
[SPEAKER_00] navještanje silnih dijela, izlazak iz tame u svjetlo.

61
00:05:12,759 --> 00:05:17,079
[SPEAKER_00] Jel mi tako izgledamo? Ajmo iskreno.

62
00:05:20,300 --> 00:05:21,879
[SPEAKER_00] A mi smo pozvani to biti.

63
00:05:21,879 --> 00:05:30,040
[SPEAKER_00] Ali potrebno je da nam duh sveti iznova otkrije naš poziv.

64
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:35,600
[SPEAKER_00] Kad se to dogodi, onda se događaju i čudesa, onda se događaju i obračenja,

65
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:37,399
[SPEAKER_00] onda se događa i posvečenja.

66
00:05:38,660 --> 00:05:42,220
[SPEAKER_00] I mi moramo ponovo počet živjeti tu svoju ulogu.

67
00:05:42,220 --> 00:05:46,879
[SPEAKER_00] To će se najprije očitovat u našem odnosu s Bogom.

68
00:05:48,540 --> 00:05:51,199
[SPEAKER_00] Znate, mi u Zagrebu to zovemo zlatna mladež.

69
00:05:51,199 --> 00:05:54,800
[SPEAKER_00] Vjeratno je vi imate one sinove, či su očevi jako bogati,

70
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:56,680
[SPEAKER_00] koji zbog toga vozi skupa auta.

71
00:05:56,680 --> 00:05:58,379
[SPEAKER_00] I kako se oni ponašaju?

72
00:05:58,379 --> 00:06:00,360
[SPEAKER_00] Malo i bahato, jel da?

73
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:01,899
[SPEAKER_00] Ulaze di god oče.

74
00:06:01,899 --> 00:06:07,060
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto? Znate li znaju da će se njihov otac pobrinut za njih?

75
00:06:07,060 --> 00:06:09,500
[SPEAKER_00] Iako je to negativan primjer,

76
00:06:09,500 --> 00:06:11,800
[SPEAKER_00] iz svih primjera, kaže sveti Alfons Ligori,

77
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:13,639
[SPEAKER_00] i to je jedna od znakova poniznosti,

78
00:06:13,639 --> 00:06:15,279
[SPEAKER_00] možemo i moramo učiti.

79
00:06:15,899 --> 00:06:19,319
[SPEAKER_00] Tako bi se mi trebali odnositi prema našem nebeskom otcu.

80
00:06:19,319 --> 00:06:21,800
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže poslanica Hebrejima,

81
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:24,920
[SPEAKER_00] pristupajmo dakle smijelo prijestolju milosti,

82
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:26,980
[SPEAKER_00] da primimo milosrđe i milost

83
00:06:26,980 --> 00:06:29,160
[SPEAKER_00] i nađemo pomoć za pravi čas.

84
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:30,779
[SPEAKER_00] Smijelo, s pouzdanjem,

85
00:06:30,779 --> 00:06:32,300
[SPEAKER_00] jer ja znam ko je moj otac,

86
00:06:32,300 --> 00:06:33,959
[SPEAKER_00] a i znam kako on gleda na mene.

87
00:06:33,959 --> 00:06:38,459
[SPEAKER_00] I kad se to očito je u našem odnosu s Bogom,

88
00:06:38,459 --> 00:06:40,579
[SPEAKER_00] koji trebamo izgrađivati na taj način,

89
00:06:40,579 --> 00:06:45,079
[SPEAKER_00] onda će se to kasnije preliti na naše odnose s ljudima,

90
00:06:45,079 --> 00:06:48,920
[SPEAKER_00] pa i naše odnose sa svojim susjedima koji ovdje žive,

91
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:50,220
[SPEAKER_00] koji možda nisu u vjeri.

92
00:06:50,220 --> 00:06:56,259
[SPEAKER_00] Glavni problem je što mi ne vjerujemo.

93
00:06:56,259 --> 00:06:58,019
[SPEAKER_00] Mi vjerujemo u Boga,

94
00:06:58,019 --> 00:06:59,939
[SPEAKER_00] ali ne vjerujemo Bogu da je to moguće

95
00:06:59,939 --> 00:07:01,819
[SPEAKER_00] i da je moguće da se dogodi preko nas.

96
00:07:03,180 --> 00:07:06,939
[SPEAKER_00] Ovdje je većina pravoslavna u ovoj općini,

97
00:07:06,939 --> 00:07:09,540
[SPEAKER_00] znači većinski je srpsko stanovništvo,

98
00:07:09,540 --> 00:07:15,420
[SPEAKER_00] i često mi zapravo ne vjerujemo da možemo puno ovdje evangelizirati,

99
00:07:15,420 --> 00:07:17,139
[SPEAKER_00] ali vjerujte mi i tekako možemo.

100
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:21,939
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što sam čuo kroz godinu dana što pomažemo i dijelujemo na ovoj župi,

101
00:07:21,939 --> 00:07:27,420
[SPEAKER_00] da su mnogi pravoslavci gledajući vas i vaše odlaske na nedeljnu misu,

102
00:07:27,420 --> 00:07:29,639
[SPEAKER_00] počeli odlaziti na nedeljnu liturgiju.

103
00:07:31,019 --> 00:07:32,939
[SPEAKER_00] Zato li je to zasvjetljilo kao znak?

104
00:07:32,939 --> 00:07:37,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ajmo još viš, što oni još mogu naučiti od vas?

105
00:07:37,300 --> 00:07:41,480
[SPEAKER_00] Zar ćete ostati na tome da mogu naučiti samo od vas?

106
00:07:41,480 --> 00:07:43,839
[SPEAKER_00] Idemo obaviti nedeljnu misu.

107
00:07:43,839 --> 00:07:47,199
[SPEAKER_00] Vidite, nije bitno di ste,

108
00:07:47,199 --> 00:07:49,860
[SPEAKER_00] nego je bitno di je vaše srce

109
00:07:49,860 --> 00:07:52,240
[SPEAKER_00] i di je vaše srce u odnosu na Boga.

110
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:56,319
[SPEAKER_00] Sveti Augustin kaže da će Bog biti točno onoliko velik

111
00:07:56,319 --> 00:07:59,980
[SPEAKER_00] u našem životu, koliko mu naša vjera to dopusti.

112
00:08:00,939 --> 00:08:02,639
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo ti koji određujemo mjeru.

113
00:08:02,639 --> 00:08:05,480
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je svemoguć.

114
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kolika je tvoja vjera?

115
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:11,279
[SPEAKER_00] I mi smo kao lajci,

116
00:08:11,279 --> 00:08:14,379
[SPEAKER_00] evo danes je evanđelje bilo upučeno lajcima,

117
00:08:14,379 --> 00:08:16,980
[SPEAKER_00] često imamo jednu povlaštenu ulogu.

118
00:08:16,980 --> 00:08:19,660
[SPEAKER_00] Jer možemo doći tamo gdje svećenici ne mogu doći.

119
00:08:19,660 --> 00:08:22,720
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ljudi imaju često predrasudu prema svećeniku.

120
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:25,800
[SPEAKER_00] Mi trebamo postati taj most

121
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:29,500
[SPEAKER_00] između tih periferija, kako ih naziva Papa Franjo,

122
00:08:30,860 --> 00:08:34,440
[SPEAKER_00] i sakramenata u kojima je spasenje, u kojima je život.

123
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:41,620
[SPEAKER_00] Dokument Lumen Gentium se između ostalog obraća lajcima

124
00:08:41,620 --> 00:08:43,980
[SPEAKER_00] i govori također o kraljevskoj službi.

125
00:08:44,399 --> 00:08:49,299
[SPEAKER_00] Htio bih vam jedan citat koje mene posebno dotakne ostaviti na srce.

126
00:08:49,299 --> 00:08:51,220
[SPEAKER_00] I malo ćemo ga raščlaniti.

127
00:08:54,279 --> 00:08:58,659
[SPEAKER_00] Krist je postavsi poslušan sve do smrti, te zbog toga uzvišen od oca,

128
00:08:58,659 --> 00:09:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] to je 36. točka dokumenta, ušao u slavu svojega kraljevstva.

129
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:09,279
[SPEAKER_00] Njemu je sve podvrgnuto, a on će sebe i sve stvoreno podvrći ocu,

130
00:09:09,279 --> 00:09:10,720
[SPEAKER_00] da bude Bog sve u svemu.

131
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:17,600
[SPEAKER_00] Tu je vlast, on poda učenicima, da i oni, to znači vi, to znači mi,

132
00:09:18,539 --> 00:09:20,860
[SPEAKER_00] budu postavljeni u kraljevsku slobodu,

133
00:09:20,860 --> 00:09:26,720
[SPEAKER_00] te samo odricanjem i svetim životom u sebi pobjede kraljevstvo grijeha,

134
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:30,340
[SPEAKER_00] što više, da služeći Kristu u drugima,

135
00:09:30,340 --> 00:09:35,720
[SPEAKER_00] po niznošću i strpljivošću privedu svoju braću onom kralju

136
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:39,139
[SPEAKER_00] kojemu služiti znači kraljevati.

137
00:09:39,139 --> 00:09:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kako jak tekst.

138
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:47,759
[SPEAKER_00] Htio bih vam nekoliko riječi koji su meni baš puno znače

139
00:09:47,759 --> 00:09:50,940
[SPEAKER_00] i kroz kojem je Bog progovorio staviti vama na srce.

140
00:09:50,940 --> 00:09:54,059
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo kaže, tu je vlast, on poda učenicima,

141
00:09:54,059 --> 00:09:56,759
[SPEAKER_00] da oni budu postavljeni u kraljevsku slobodu.

142
00:09:56,759 --> 00:09:58,440
[SPEAKER_00] E to je to o čem pričamo.

143
00:09:58,440 --> 00:10:01,500
[SPEAKER_00] Kraljevska sloboda. To se na nama mora vidjeti.

144
00:10:01,500 --> 00:10:07,440
[SPEAKER_00] Mi često, kao katolici, pogrešno shvatimo poniznost.

145
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:11,799
[SPEAKER_00] I onda postajemo antireklama za Božje kraljevstvo.

146
00:10:11,799 --> 00:10:17,679
[SPEAKER_00] Kakva su vaša lica kad izlazite iz crkve u svijet?

147
00:10:17,759 --> 00:10:22,779
[SPEAKER_00] Mojsije kad se susrao sa Bogom, lice mu je tako svjetlilo

148
00:10:22,779 --> 00:10:28,019
[SPEAKER_00] da mu je trebao privjes oko lica jer ljudi nisu mogli gledati u njegovo lice.

149
00:10:28,019 --> 00:10:34,620
[SPEAKER_00] Kraljevska sloboda. Kraljevska sloboda privlači.

150
00:10:34,620 --> 00:10:40,059
[SPEAKER_00] Poniznost se često doživljava kao umanjivanje samog sebe.

151
00:10:41,059 --> 00:10:44,159
[SPEAKER_00] Evo što C.S. Lewis kaže, što je to prava poniznost.

152
00:10:44,159 --> 00:10:48,080
[SPEAKER_00] I to je ona poniznost koja se na nama treba vidjeti.

153
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:52,720
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, nemojte misliti ako susretnete istinski poniznog čovjeka,

154
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:56,320
[SPEAKER_00] da će on biti ono što većina ljudi danas naziva poniznim.

155
00:10:57,279 --> 00:11:02,419
[SPEAKER_00] On neće biti sladunjava ulizica koja vam uvijek govori da je on naravno niko i ništa.

156
00:11:03,259 --> 00:11:09,059
[SPEAKER_00] Vjerojatno, sve što ćete vi misliti o njemu je to da on sliči veselom, inteligentnom momku

157
00:11:09,059 --> 00:11:12,340
[SPEAKER_00] kojeg je stvarno zainteresiralo ono što ste mu vi rekli.

158
00:11:12,340 --> 00:11:18,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ako vam se on ne svidi, to će biti zato što se osjećate pomalo zavidni nekome

159
00:11:18,519 --> 00:11:22,980
[SPEAKER_00] koji, kako se čini, slakoćom uživa u životu.

160
00:11:24,980 --> 00:11:30,039
[SPEAKER_00] On neće misliti o poniznosti, nego on neće uopće misliti o sebi.

161
00:11:30,039 --> 00:11:34,159
[SPEAKER_00] Užitak života.

162
00:11:34,159 --> 00:11:39,519
[SPEAKER_00] Mi možemo predstavljati užitak života.

163
00:11:39,519 --> 00:11:44,600
[SPEAKER_00] Zato je li uživamo ako smo Boži dobra ove zemlje,

164
00:11:44,600 --> 00:11:47,620
[SPEAKER_00] ali nas ona nisu zarobili, mi smo njihovi gospodari.

165
00:11:47,620 --> 00:11:52,120
[SPEAKER_00] I to treba biti ta kraljevska sloboda od navezanosti.

166
00:11:54,980 --> 00:11:57,179
[SPEAKER_00] Šta mislite?

167
00:11:57,179 --> 00:12:02,299
[SPEAKER_00] Kako je Isus izgledao dok je hodao ovom zemlje?

168
00:12:02,299 --> 00:12:04,259
[SPEAKER_00] On je imao to u krajevsku, on je imao to.

169
00:12:04,259 --> 00:12:05,740
[SPEAKER_00] On je bio sin očev.

170
00:12:05,740 --> 00:12:10,799
[SPEAKER_00] I često su ga krivo tumačili, kao što će i vas, ako budete slobodni.

171
00:12:10,799 --> 00:12:14,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo malo uči u jedan događaj sad.

172
00:12:14,159 --> 00:12:18,080
[SPEAKER_00] Probajte se zamisliti da ste vi židov

173
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:20,960
[SPEAKER_00] koji živi u vrijeme kad Isus radi čuda.

174
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:22,220
[SPEAKER_00] Isus je kontroverzan.

175
00:12:22,720 --> 00:12:25,960
[SPEAKER_00] Duhovni autoriteti tog vremena su protiv njega.

176
00:12:25,960 --> 00:12:28,080
[SPEAKER_00] To vam odmah pali alarm.

177
00:12:28,080 --> 00:12:32,059
[SPEAKER_00] Pa gle, veliki svećenik je protiv njega, farizeji koji žive sve to,

178
00:12:32,059 --> 00:12:33,820
[SPEAKER_00] tu vjerojatno nešto smrdi.

179
00:12:33,820 --> 00:12:37,500
[SPEAKER_00] A s druge strane poznajte neke prijatelje

180
00:12:37,500 --> 00:12:40,919
[SPEAKER_00] koji su čudesno ozdravili, koji su malom promijenio život.

181
00:12:40,919 --> 00:12:41,960
[SPEAKER_00] I to ste isto čuli.

182
00:12:43,720 --> 00:12:46,559
[SPEAKER_00] I vi želite donijet svoj sud.

183
00:12:46,559 --> 00:12:47,279
[SPEAKER_00] Ko je Isus?

184
00:12:47,279 --> 00:12:49,299
[SPEAKER_00] Ko je ta Isus Hrist?

185
00:12:49,299 --> 00:12:52,419
[SPEAKER_00] I zamislite se recimo da dođete onaj događaj

186
00:12:52,419 --> 00:12:54,620
[SPEAKER_00] prije Isusove muke i smrti,

187
00:12:54,620 --> 00:12:56,799
[SPEAKER_00] kad je Isus u Lazarovoj kući.

188
00:12:56,799 --> 00:13:00,779
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo što je sumnjio, evo,

189
00:13:00,779 --> 00:13:03,559
[SPEAKER_00] on je sad tog frajera uskrisio pred nekoliko dana.

190
00:13:03,559 --> 00:13:04,960
[SPEAKER_00] On je bio mrtav četiri dana,

191
00:13:04,960 --> 00:13:07,899
[SPEAKER_00] uskrišen je onako dosta snažan događaj.

192
00:13:08,299 --> 00:13:09,799
[SPEAKER_00] Sigrano bi crv sumnjao vama,

193
00:13:09,799 --> 00:13:13,580
[SPEAKER_00] pa zašto je baš uskrisio jednog od najbogatijih židova?

194
00:13:13,580 --> 00:13:16,120
[SPEAKER_00] Što nije mogao uskrisiti nekog siromaha?

195
00:13:16,120 --> 00:13:17,679
[SPEAKER_00] Koja je tu računica?

196
00:13:17,679 --> 00:13:19,879
[SPEAKER_00] I sad eto, oni baš sjede za stolom,

197
00:13:19,879 --> 00:13:20,740
[SPEAKER_00] jedan do drugog.

198
00:13:20,740 --> 00:13:24,860
[SPEAKER_00] I onda dolazi Marija Magdalena,

199
00:13:24,860 --> 00:13:26,960
[SPEAKER_00] koja je bila poznata kao javna bludnica,

200
00:13:26,960 --> 00:13:29,759
[SPEAKER_00] nešto ko Severina u naše vrijeme

201
00:13:29,759 --> 00:13:31,379
[SPEAKER_00] ili neka takva dama.

202
00:13:31,379 --> 00:13:32,980
[SPEAKER_00] Sad eto, baš ona oko njega

203
00:13:32,980 --> 00:13:37,720
[SPEAKER_00] i ona nosi alabasternu posudu

204
00:13:37,720 --> 00:13:39,559
[SPEAKER_00] miomirisne pomasti.

205
00:13:39,559 --> 00:13:41,899
[SPEAKER_00] A to mi je vrijedilo,

206
00:13:41,899 --> 00:13:43,559
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam koliko bi to bilo provedeno

207
00:13:43,559 --> 00:13:44,340
[SPEAKER_00] u današnji jezik,

208
00:13:44,340 --> 00:13:45,240
[SPEAKER_00] tisuća eura.

209
00:13:45,240 --> 00:13:48,399
[SPEAKER_00] To je oko ono kad imate ulje od lavande,

210
00:13:48,399 --> 00:13:49,539
[SPEAKER_00] stavite jednu kap.

211
00:13:49,539 --> 00:13:51,379
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto litra ulja lavande

212
00:13:51,379 --> 00:13:52,779
[SPEAKER_00] košta deset tisuća eura?

213
00:13:52,779 --> 00:13:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa zato li jednu kap stavite u parfum

214
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:56,080
[SPEAKER_00] i već je intenzivno.

215
00:13:56,080 --> 00:13:59,279
[SPEAKER_00] I tako ona dolazi sa tom skupom

216
00:13:59,279 --> 00:14:00,480
[SPEAKER_00] miomirisnom pomasti,

217
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:02,860
[SPEAKER_00] baš ona je to bludnica,

218
00:14:02,860 --> 00:14:07,019
[SPEAKER_00] i razbije to izlijemu na glavu.

219
00:14:07,139 --> 00:14:09,360
[SPEAKER_00] I sad Isus onako fin nageliran,

220
00:14:09,360 --> 00:14:12,539
[SPEAKER_00] probajte misliti kako je mirice širi oko njega,

221
00:14:12,539 --> 00:14:13,679
[SPEAKER_00] tamo šeće okolo,

222
00:14:13,679 --> 00:14:14,980
[SPEAKER_00] i dolazi Juda,

223
00:14:14,980 --> 00:14:18,980
[SPEAKER_00] a kraljevska sloboda nam upravo

224
00:14:18,980 --> 00:14:20,259
[SPEAKER_00] omogućuje da gledamo

225
00:14:20,259 --> 00:14:21,759
[SPEAKER_00] pozadinu stvari,

226
00:14:21,759 --> 00:14:22,440
[SPEAKER_00] onu istinu,

227
00:14:22,440 --> 00:14:23,460
[SPEAKER_00] a ne ono naliće,

228
00:14:23,460 --> 00:14:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] koje kao smokvino lišće sjaji okolo.

229
00:14:26,399 --> 00:14:28,740
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi Juda i kaže,

230
00:14:28,740 --> 00:14:30,279
[SPEAKER_00] a vi to slušate,

231
00:14:30,279 --> 00:14:34,379
[SPEAKER_00] pa šta nismo mogli prodat tu pomast

232
00:14:34,379 --> 00:14:36,120
[SPEAKER_00] i dat siromasima.

233
00:14:36,120 --> 00:14:38,100
[SPEAKER_00] Kako lijepo to zvuči, jel da?

234
00:14:38,100 --> 00:14:41,080
[SPEAKER_00] Juda je baš pravi socijalist,

235
00:14:41,080 --> 00:14:43,039
[SPEAKER_00] onako, baš lijepo to zvuči,

236
00:14:43,120 --> 00:14:44,879
[SPEAKER_00] dajmo to prodati i dat siromasima.

237
00:14:44,879 --> 00:14:45,759
[SPEAKER_00] Ali,

238
00:14:45,759 --> 00:14:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Isus poznaje naliće stvari,

239
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:49,340
[SPEAKER_00] i lice i naliće.

240
00:14:49,340 --> 00:14:50,740
[SPEAKER_00] I on zna da Juda to kaže

241
00:14:50,740 --> 00:14:51,480
[SPEAKER_00] zato je odkrade,

242
00:14:51,480 --> 00:14:52,279
[SPEAKER_00] ali vi ne znate.

243
00:14:55,340 --> 00:14:56,340
[SPEAKER_00] On dođe,

244
00:14:56,340 --> 00:14:57,679
[SPEAKER_00] takav nageliran,

245
00:14:57,679 --> 00:14:58,919
[SPEAKER_00] u kući bogataša,

246
00:14:58,919 --> 00:14:59,940
[SPEAKER_00] pokre bludnice,

247
00:14:59,940 --> 00:15:01,500
[SPEAKER_00] oko njega mio miris

248
00:15:01,500 --> 00:15:01,879
[SPEAKER_00] i kaže,

249
00:15:01,879 --> 00:15:03,779
[SPEAKER_00] siromaha ćete uvijek imat.

250
00:15:03,779 --> 00:15:06,940
[SPEAKER_00] Šta bi vi mislili o Isusu?

251
00:15:06,940 --> 00:15:09,440
[SPEAKER_00] Da Isusov primjer

252
00:15:09,440 --> 00:15:10,899
[SPEAKER_00] nije nekad bio i sablažnjiv,

253
00:15:10,899 --> 00:15:12,440
[SPEAKER_00] pa ne bi rekao

254
00:15:12,440 --> 00:15:13,500
[SPEAKER_00] u Evanđelju,

255
00:15:13,500 --> 00:15:15,419
[SPEAKER_00] ja onom ko se sablazni o mene.

256
00:15:15,419 --> 00:15:17,759
[SPEAKER_00] I ta vaša sloboda

257
00:15:17,759 --> 00:15:18,919
[SPEAKER_00] može provocirat

258
00:15:18,919 --> 00:15:19,679
[SPEAKER_00] i bolje,

259
00:15:19,679 --> 00:15:20,759
[SPEAKER_00] neka provocira.

260
00:15:20,759 --> 00:15:23,919
[SPEAKER_00] Zato je li vaš život

261
00:15:23,919 --> 00:15:25,100
[SPEAKER_00] mora postati,

262
00:15:25,100 --> 00:15:26,899
[SPEAKER_00] u ljudima budit pitanja.

263
00:15:26,899 --> 00:15:29,159
[SPEAKER_00] Di je izvor te slobode?

264
00:15:29,159 --> 00:15:31,059
[SPEAKER_00] Što taj čovjek ima

265
00:15:31,059 --> 00:15:32,740
[SPEAKER_00] kad može tako živjeti?

266
00:15:32,740 --> 00:15:34,980
[SPEAKER_00] To ono što

267
00:15:34,980 --> 00:15:35,899
[SPEAKER_00] Paul Clodell,

268
00:15:35,899 --> 00:15:36,899
[SPEAKER_00] francuski filozof,

269
00:15:36,899 --> 00:15:37,700
[SPEAKER_00] kaže sjajno,

270
00:15:37,700 --> 00:15:39,139
[SPEAKER_00] nemojte ljudima

271
00:15:39,139 --> 00:15:40,220
[SPEAKER_00] govoriti o Bogu,

272
00:15:40,220 --> 00:15:42,120
[SPEAKER_00] nego živite tako

273
00:15:42,120 --> 00:15:43,340
[SPEAKER_00] da vas oni pitaju

274
00:15:43,340 --> 00:15:44,279
[SPEAKER_00] o Bogu.

275
00:15:44,279 --> 00:15:50,759
[SPEAKER_00] Kraljevska sloboda.

276
00:15:50,759 --> 00:15:54,860
[SPEAKER_00] Dalje,

277
00:15:54,860 --> 00:15:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] papa Pavao VI

278
00:15:59,000 --> 00:16:01,240
[SPEAKER_00] kaže

279
00:16:01,240 --> 00:16:02,279
[SPEAKER_00] da je postavljeni se

280
00:16:02,279 --> 00:16:03,440
[SPEAKER_00] u kraljevsku slobodu

281
00:16:03,440 --> 00:16:04,919
[SPEAKER_00] te samoodricanjem

282
00:16:04,919 --> 00:16:06,379
[SPEAKER_00] i svetim životom.

283
00:16:06,379 --> 00:16:09,740
[SPEAKER_00] Samoodricanje

284
00:16:09,740 --> 00:16:10,759
[SPEAKER_00] i svet život.

285
00:16:10,759 --> 00:16:12,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ta sloboda,

286
00:16:12,460 --> 00:16:13,279
[SPEAKER_00] naravno,

287
00:16:13,279 --> 00:16:14,720
[SPEAKER_00] neće biti nama izgovor

288
00:16:14,720 --> 00:16:15,539
[SPEAKER_00] da se ponašamo

289
00:16:15,539 --> 00:16:16,039
[SPEAKER_00] bahato,

290
00:16:16,100 --> 00:16:17,019
[SPEAKER_00] moramo biti svjesni

291
00:16:17,019 --> 00:16:18,019
[SPEAKER_00] da naš kralj ima

292
00:16:18,019 --> 00:16:18,679
[SPEAKER_00] dvije krune.

293
00:16:18,679 --> 00:16:20,059
[SPEAKER_00] I onu zlatnu

294
00:16:20,059 --> 00:16:20,860
[SPEAKER_00] proslavljenu,

295
00:16:20,860 --> 00:16:21,879
[SPEAKER_00] ali i onu trnovu.

296
00:16:21,879 --> 00:16:24,799
[SPEAKER_00] I ono što je bitno,

297
00:16:24,799 --> 00:16:25,899
[SPEAKER_00] ako ti to imaš,

298
00:16:25,899 --> 00:16:27,740
[SPEAKER_00] a to je velečasni,

299
00:16:27,740 --> 00:16:28,600
[SPEAKER_00] sjajno dotaknuo

300
00:16:28,600 --> 00:16:29,340
[SPEAKER_00] na propovjedi,

301
00:16:29,340 --> 00:16:31,799
[SPEAKER_00] ti moraš to podijeliti.

302
00:16:32,759 --> 00:16:34,120
[SPEAKER_00] I to je to samoodricanje

303
00:16:34,120 --> 00:16:34,879
[SPEAKER_00] i svet život.

304
00:16:34,879 --> 00:16:36,080
[SPEAKER_00] U Bibliji

305
00:16:36,080 --> 00:16:38,399
[SPEAKER_00] imamo na više mjesta

306
00:16:38,399 --> 00:16:39,580
[SPEAKER_00] roba i sina.

307
00:16:39,580 --> 00:16:40,879
[SPEAKER_00] I sveti Pavol

308
00:16:40,879 --> 00:16:41,960
[SPEAKER_00] naglašava da mi trebamo

309
00:16:41,960 --> 00:16:42,500
[SPEAKER_00] prebom Bogu

310
00:16:42,500 --> 00:16:43,139
[SPEAKER_00] biti sina,

311
00:16:43,139 --> 00:16:43,720
[SPEAKER_00] ne rob.

312
00:16:43,720 --> 00:16:45,240
[SPEAKER_00] A znate kako se sin

313
00:16:45,240 --> 00:16:46,299
[SPEAKER_00] ponaša u to vrijeme?

314
00:16:46,299 --> 00:16:47,360
[SPEAKER_00] Sin koji je nasljednik

315
00:16:47,360 --> 00:16:47,860
[SPEAKER_00] i manja.

316
00:16:47,860 --> 00:16:50,120
[SPEAKER_00] Dolazio je prije svih robova

317
00:16:50,120 --> 00:16:50,940
[SPEAKER_00] na posao,

318
00:16:50,940 --> 00:16:54,100
[SPEAKER_00] pratio je sve što robovi čine

319
00:16:54,100 --> 00:16:56,039
[SPEAKER_00] i osto bi zadnji poslije

320
00:16:56,039 --> 00:16:57,039
[SPEAKER_00] provjeriti

321
00:16:57,039 --> 00:16:58,700
[SPEAKER_00] je li sve bilo u redu.

322
00:16:58,700 --> 00:17:01,559
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, to je i odgovornost.

323
00:17:01,559 --> 00:17:03,379
[SPEAKER_00] Odgovornost nad onim

324
00:17:03,379 --> 00:17:04,380
[SPEAKER_00] što vam je povjereno.

325
00:17:04,380 --> 00:17:06,160
[SPEAKER_00] Ta vaša sloboda

326
00:17:06,160 --> 00:17:07,200
[SPEAKER_00] nije izgovor tijelu,

327
00:17:07,200 --> 00:17:08,440
[SPEAKER_00] kao što kaže Pavao,

328
00:17:08,440 --> 00:17:10,039
[SPEAKER_00] nego budi u nama

329
00:17:10,039 --> 00:17:11,720
[SPEAKER_00] tu odgovornost

330
00:17:11,720 --> 00:17:13,359
[SPEAKER_00] za baštinu

331
00:17:13,359 --> 00:17:14,359
[SPEAKER_00] koja nam je ostavljena.

332
00:17:14,359 --> 00:17:15,299
[SPEAKER_00] Da ne budemo kao

333
00:17:15,299 --> 00:17:16,480
[SPEAKER_00] vinogradari ubojice.

334
00:17:23,920 --> 00:17:26,140
[SPEAKER_00] Kraljevsku slobodu

335
00:17:26,140 --> 00:17:26,960
[SPEAKER_00] sa modricanjem

336
00:17:26,960 --> 00:17:27,980
[SPEAKER_00] i svetim životom

337
00:17:27,980 --> 00:17:29,140
[SPEAKER_00] u sebi pobjede

338
00:17:29,140 --> 00:17:30,220
[SPEAKER_00] kraljevstvo grijeha.

339
00:17:30,220 --> 00:17:32,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je baš snažna rečenica.

340
00:17:32,039 --> 00:17:32,859
[SPEAKER_00] Zato,

341
00:17:32,859 --> 00:17:35,380
[SPEAKER_00] jer se sa grijehom

342
00:17:35,380 --> 00:17:36,160
[SPEAKER_00] možemo suočiti

343
00:17:36,160 --> 00:17:37,039
[SPEAKER_00] na dva načina.

344
00:17:37,039 --> 00:17:39,099
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan je dobar,

345
00:17:39,099 --> 00:17:39,900
[SPEAKER_00] drugi je bolji.

346
00:17:39,900 --> 00:17:41,920
[SPEAKER_00] Vi možete,

347
00:17:41,920 --> 00:17:43,240
[SPEAKER_00] kad je grijeh u pitanju,

348
00:17:43,240 --> 00:17:44,720
[SPEAKER_00] bježati od grijeha.

349
00:17:44,720 --> 00:17:45,700
[SPEAKER_00] I to nije loše.

350
00:17:45,700 --> 00:17:48,619
[SPEAKER_00] To nije loše.

351
00:17:48,619 --> 00:17:49,119
[SPEAKER_00] Isus kaže

352
00:17:49,119 --> 00:17:50,299
[SPEAKER_00] ako te oko sablažnjava

353
00:17:50,299 --> 00:17:50,940
[SPEAKER_00] iskopaj ga.

354
00:17:50,940 --> 00:17:52,380
[SPEAKER_00] Maknis,

355
00:17:52,380 --> 00:17:53,180
[SPEAKER_00] ako imaš problema

356
00:17:53,180 --> 00:17:53,859
[SPEAKER_00] s alkoholom,

357
00:17:53,859 --> 00:17:54,480
[SPEAKER_00] nemoj otić

358
00:17:54,480 --> 00:17:55,940
[SPEAKER_00] na neku pijanku

359
00:17:55,940 --> 00:17:56,480
[SPEAKER_00] di znaš

360
00:17:56,480 --> 00:17:57,319
[SPEAKER_00] da će se pit.

361
00:17:57,319 --> 00:18:01,539
[SPEAKER_00] To je jedan način.

362
00:18:01,539 --> 00:18:03,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ali drugi je puno,

363
00:18:03,019 --> 00:18:03,940
[SPEAKER_00] puno snažniji.

364
00:18:03,940 --> 00:18:05,319
[SPEAKER_00] A to je da ti

365
00:18:05,319 --> 00:18:06,140
[SPEAKER_00] iznutra

366
00:18:06,140 --> 00:18:06,980
[SPEAKER_00] u sebi

367
00:18:06,980 --> 00:18:07,759
[SPEAKER_00] pobjediš

368
00:18:07,759 --> 00:18:08,799
[SPEAKER_00] kraljevstvo grijeha.

