00:31:09,099 --> 00:31:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Male ptice,

808
00:31:11,000 --> 00:31:13,279
[SPEAKER_00] kao što su golubovi,

809
00:31:13,279 --> 00:31:15,160
[SPEAKER_00] počinju jako brzo

810
00:31:15,160 --> 00:31:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] mahat krilima

811
00:31:16,000 --> 00:31:17,579
[SPEAKER_00] i pošto puše jak vjetar,

812
00:31:17,579 --> 00:31:21,259
[SPEAKER_00] oni više ne mogu to izdržati

813
00:31:21,259 --> 00:31:23,180
[SPEAKER_00] i sklone se onda u neke rupe

814
00:31:23,180 --> 00:31:24,859
[SPEAKER_00] jer su išli svojim snagama.

815
00:31:24,859 --> 00:31:27,059
[SPEAKER_00] A orao

816
00:31:27,059 --> 00:31:30,299
[SPEAKER_00] dopušta da ga upravo ta jaka stroja

817
00:31:30,299 --> 00:31:31,799
[SPEAKER_00] podigne na višu visinu,

818
00:31:31,799 --> 00:31:33,900
[SPEAKER_00] dođe iznad oblaka

819
00:31:33,900 --> 00:31:35,059
[SPEAKER_00] i otvori krila

820
00:31:35,059 --> 00:31:36,880
[SPEAKER_00] i prepusti se

821
00:31:36,880 --> 00:31:39,500
[SPEAKER_00] da ga ta stroja nosi.

822
00:31:39,500 --> 00:31:42,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ove ptice kad glede orlovu lakoću

823
00:31:42,559 --> 00:31:44,180
[SPEAKER_00] ne zna odakle mu to.

824
00:31:44,180 --> 00:31:45,180
[SPEAKER_00] dive se orlu

825
00:31:45,180 --> 00:31:47,740
[SPEAKER_00] i misle da je to njegova snaga,

826
00:31:47,740 --> 00:31:48,240
[SPEAKER_00] ali nije.

827
00:31:48,240 --> 00:31:49,980
[SPEAKER_00] On je samo znao

828
00:31:49,980 --> 00:31:50,960
[SPEAKER_00] raširit krila

829
00:31:50,960 --> 00:31:52,799
[SPEAKER_00] i pušti da ga ta struja nosi.

830
00:31:52,799 --> 00:31:55,220
[SPEAKER_00] E tako i vi trebate

831
00:31:55,220 --> 00:31:57,240
[SPEAKER_00] neugodnosti oluje

832
00:31:57,240 --> 00:31:58,180
[SPEAKER_00] vašeg života

833
00:31:58,180 --> 00:32:00,059
[SPEAKER_00] pretvoriti u struju

834
00:32:00,059 --> 00:32:01,160
[SPEAKER_00] koja će vas donijet

835
00:32:01,160 --> 00:32:03,119
[SPEAKER_00] i dat vam jednu ptiću perspektivu,

836
00:32:03,119 --> 00:32:04,180
[SPEAKER_00] jedan novi pogled

837
00:32:04,180 --> 00:32:05,039
[SPEAKER_00] da iza te oluje

838
00:32:05,039 --> 00:32:06,519
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi sunce i bistrina.

839
00:32:07,220 --> 00:32:08,920
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što kaže Salomon

840
00:32:08,920 --> 00:32:11,839
[SPEAKER_00] da je kraljevo srce

841
00:32:11,839 --> 00:32:12,940
[SPEAKER_00] u ruci jahvinoj

842
00:32:12,940 --> 00:32:14,180
[SPEAKER_00] kao voda tekućica.

843
00:32:14,180 --> 00:32:16,500
[SPEAKER_00] Vodi ga kuda on hoće.

844
00:32:16,500 --> 00:32:19,420
[SPEAKER_00] Prepoznajte Boga

845
00:32:19,420 --> 00:32:20,579
[SPEAKER_00] u svakoj okolnosti

846
00:32:20,579 --> 00:32:21,400
[SPEAKER_00] vašeg života.

847
00:32:21,400 --> 00:32:25,660
[SPEAKER_00] Prepoznajte Božje djelovanje

848
00:32:25,660 --> 00:32:26,799
[SPEAKER_00] olu i nek vas ono

849
00:32:26,799 --> 00:32:28,200
[SPEAKER_00] uzdigne vašu dušu.

850
00:32:28,200 --> 00:32:32,619
[SPEAKER_00] I onda ćete mnogo jasnije vidjeti

851
00:32:32,619 --> 00:32:33,759
[SPEAKER_00] što i zašto je

852
00:32:33,759 --> 00:32:35,960
[SPEAKER_00] se događa ovdje.

853
00:32:36,440 --> 00:32:37,200
[SPEAKER_00] Onda ćete biti

854
00:32:37,200 --> 00:32:38,420
[SPEAKER_00] proročki narod.

855
00:32:38,420 --> 00:32:41,420
[SPEAKER_00] Onda će Bog s vama

856
00:32:41,420 --> 00:32:42,200
[SPEAKER_00] podijeliti

857
00:32:42,200 --> 00:32:43,660
[SPEAKER_00] kao sa svetim Josipom

858
00:32:43,660 --> 00:32:44,539
[SPEAKER_00] šta se događa.

859
00:32:44,539 --> 00:32:47,279
[SPEAKER_00] Kad je Bog odlučio

860
00:32:47,279 --> 00:32:48,779
[SPEAKER_00] Sodomu

861
00:32:48,779 --> 00:32:50,059
[SPEAKER_00] uništit

862
00:32:50,059 --> 00:32:51,079
[SPEAKER_00] on kaže

863
00:32:51,079 --> 00:32:51,960
[SPEAKER_00] Bog kaže

864
00:32:51,960 --> 00:32:53,579
[SPEAKER_00] zašto da skrivam

865
00:32:53,579 --> 00:32:55,420
[SPEAKER_00] od svog prijatelja Abrahama

866
00:32:55,420 --> 00:32:56,519
[SPEAKER_00] što želim učiniti.

867
00:32:56,519 --> 00:32:58,900
[SPEAKER_00] Bog ima potrebu

868
00:32:58,900 --> 00:33:00,559
[SPEAKER_00] podijeliti sa svojim prijateljem

869
00:33:00,559 --> 00:33:02,500
[SPEAKER_00] onim koji provodi vrijeme s njim

870
00:33:02,500 --> 00:33:03,819
[SPEAKER_00] i koji ga je naučio slušat.

871
00:33:03,819 --> 00:33:06,380
[SPEAKER_00] Šta želi učiniti?

872
00:33:06,380 --> 00:33:07,799
[SPEAKER_00] Prorok Amos kaže

873
00:33:07,799 --> 00:33:09,779
[SPEAKER_00] ništa ne čini Jahve Bog

874
00:33:09,779 --> 00:33:11,700
[SPEAKER_00] a da osnove ne objavi

875
00:33:11,700 --> 00:33:13,180
[SPEAKER_00] slugama svojim prorocima.

876
00:33:13,180 --> 00:33:14,099
[SPEAKER_00] To ste vi.

877
00:33:14,099 --> 00:33:15,940
[SPEAKER_00] To je bio Mojsije Vapa

878
00:33:15,940 --> 00:33:16,500
[SPEAKER_00] i u pustinji.

879
00:33:16,500 --> 00:33:18,559
[SPEAKER_00] O kad bi sav narod bio prorok.

880
00:33:18,559 --> 00:33:20,720
[SPEAKER_00] A osim kraljevske časti

881
00:33:20,720 --> 00:33:23,039
[SPEAKER_00] mi imamo i tu proročku čast.

882
00:33:23,039 --> 00:33:24,359
[SPEAKER_00] Tu proročku službu.

883
00:33:27,099 --> 00:33:29,839
[SPEAKER_00] Vi ste Boži proročki narod

884
00:33:29,839 --> 00:33:31,539
[SPEAKER_00] kraljevsko svećenstvo.

885
00:33:31,539 --> 00:33:35,440
[SPEAKER_00] Bog želi s vama podijeliti

886
00:33:35,440 --> 00:33:36,359
[SPEAKER_00] šta se događa

887
00:33:36,359 --> 00:33:38,140
[SPEAKER_00] i u svijetu i u politici.

888
00:33:41,460 --> 00:33:43,579
[SPEAKER_00] ali ako ostanemo kao golubovi

889
00:33:43,579 --> 00:33:45,039
[SPEAKER_00] koji samo mrmljaju na oluju

890
00:33:45,039 --> 00:33:45,859
[SPEAKER_00] koja se diže

891
00:33:45,859 --> 00:33:48,539
[SPEAKER_00] neće biti nikakvog ploda

892
00:33:48,539 --> 00:33:51,819
[SPEAKER_00] i sklonit ćemo se u svoja skučena skloništa

893
00:33:51,819 --> 00:33:54,740
[SPEAKER_00] i grijat ćemo svoje perije

894
00:33:54,740 --> 00:33:56,019
[SPEAKER_00] svoj skučeni svijet.

895
00:33:56,019 --> 00:34:02,220
[SPEAKER_00] Dopustite Bogu

896
00:34:02,220 --> 00:34:04,440
[SPEAKER_00] da vas ponese u svoje visine.

897
00:34:04,440 --> 00:34:08,699
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže Izaija

898
00:34:08,699 --> 00:34:10,059
[SPEAKER_00] da su Boži misli

899
00:34:10,059 --> 00:34:10,920
[SPEAKER_00] i Boži putevi

900
00:34:10,920 --> 00:34:12,320
[SPEAKER_00] iznad naših puteva.

901
00:34:12,320 --> 00:34:16,820
[SPEAKER_00] Ali u Kristu

902
00:34:16,820 --> 00:34:17,820
[SPEAKER_00] se to mijenja.

903
00:34:17,820 --> 00:34:19,079
[SPEAKER_00] Zato sveti Pavo

904
00:34:19,079 --> 00:34:20,260
[SPEAKER_00] o druge korinčenima kaže

905
00:34:20,260 --> 00:34:22,559
[SPEAKER_00] mi imamo Kristovu misao.

906
00:34:22,559 --> 00:34:24,239
[SPEAKER_00] Mi je imamo.

907
00:34:24,239 --> 00:34:26,840
[SPEAKER_00] Jer duhovan čovjek

908
00:34:26,840 --> 00:34:27,699
[SPEAKER_00] sve prosuđuje

909
00:34:27,699 --> 00:34:28,820
[SPEAKER_00] kaže sveti Pavo.

910
00:34:28,820 --> 00:34:30,860
[SPEAKER_00] Zar ne želite živjeti

911
00:34:30,860 --> 00:34:31,559
[SPEAKER_00] u toj slobodi?

912
00:34:31,559 --> 00:34:32,360
[SPEAKER_00] A imate to.

913
00:34:32,360 --> 00:34:35,639
[SPEAKER_00] Prestanite zobat kukuruz.

914
00:34:35,639 --> 00:34:38,980
[SPEAKER_00] Pozvani ste letit.

915
00:34:38,980 --> 00:34:42,400
[SPEAKER_00] I ovdje ste pozvani letit.

916
00:34:42,400 --> 00:34:44,300
[SPEAKER_00] Kad ovdje to postignete

917
00:34:44,300 --> 00:34:45,619
[SPEAKER_00] Bog će vam jasno pokazati

918
00:34:45,619 --> 00:34:46,820
[SPEAKER_00] šta i kako dalje.

919
00:34:50,260 --> 00:34:51,579
[SPEAKER_00] ako budemo blizu

920
00:34:51,579 --> 00:34:52,440
[SPEAKER_00] njegovog srca

921
00:34:52,440 --> 00:34:55,940
[SPEAKER_00] onda ćemo izdržati

922
00:34:55,940 --> 00:34:56,920
[SPEAKER_00] kad bude teško.

923
00:34:57,719 --> 00:34:59,659
[SPEAKER_00] navišću vam dva primjera.

924
00:34:59,659 --> 00:35:02,019
[SPEAKER_00] Marta je Marija

925
00:35:02,019 --> 00:35:03,199
[SPEAKER_00] i Petar i Ivan.

926
00:35:03,199 --> 00:35:09,460
[SPEAKER_00] Isus se nalazi u kući

927
00:35:09,460 --> 00:35:10,460
[SPEAKER_00] Marta i Marije.

928
00:35:10,460 --> 00:35:12,019
[SPEAKER_00] Marta je zauzeta

929
00:35:12,019 --> 00:35:13,119
[SPEAKER_00] oko posluživanja.

930
00:35:14,320 --> 00:35:15,079
[SPEAKER_00] nije to loši.

931
00:35:15,079 --> 00:35:16,760
[SPEAKER_00] Nije Isus rekao da je loši.

932
00:35:16,760 --> 00:35:19,039
[SPEAKER_00] A Marija je došla

933
00:35:19,039 --> 00:35:20,940
[SPEAKER_00] do njegovih nogu

934
00:35:20,940 --> 00:35:22,340
[SPEAKER_00] i upija

935
00:35:22,340 --> 00:35:23,800
[SPEAKER_00] njegovu ljubav,

936
00:35:23,800 --> 00:35:24,739
[SPEAKER_00] njegova znanja.

937
00:35:24,739 --> 00:35:25,800
[SPEAKER_00] Isus kaže

938
00:35:25,800 --> 00:35:27,539
[SPEAKER_00] ona je odabrala bolji dio

939
00:35:27,539 --> 00:35:28,780
[SPEAKER_00] koji se neće oduzeti.

940
00:35:28,780 --> 00:35:33,360
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo Petra i Ivana.

941
00:35:33,360 --> 00:35:35,980
[SPEAKER_00] Petar je jako hrabar.

942
00:35:35,980 --> 00:35:36,980
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže

943
00:35:36,980 --> 00:35:38,420
[SPEAKER_00] ja ću i živo dati za tebe.

944
00:35:39,699 --> 00:35:40,800
[SPEAKER_00] A on uvijek nekako ide

945
00:35:40,800 --> 00:35:41,719
[SPEAKER_00] ispred Isusa.

946
00:35:41,719 --> 00:35:43,719
[SPEAKER_00] On bi njega savjetovao.

947
00:35:43,719 --> 00:35:44,780
[SPEAKER_00] On zna bolje.

948
00:35:44,780 --> 00:35:45,599
[SPEAKER_00] On kalkulira.

949
00:35:45,599 --> 00:35:47,019
[SPEAKER_00] A šta Ivan radi

950
00:35:47,019 --> 00:35:48,440
[SPEAKER_00] na posljednjoj večeri?

951
00:35:48,440 --> 00:35:51,760
[SPEAKER_00] On je naslonio glavu

952
00:35:51,760 --> 00:35:52,780
[SPEAKER_00] na Isusovo srce

953
00:35:52,780 --> 00:35:53,300
[SPEAKER_00] i sluša.

954
00:35:53,300 --> 00:35:54,099
[SPEAKER_00] I Petar zna

955
00:35:54,099 --> 00:35:55,440
[SPEAKER_00] da je to tako.

956
00:35:55,440 --> 00:35:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] I zato on neće direktno pitati

957
00:35:57,000 --> 00:35:57,739
[SPEAKER_00] Isusa neko kaže

958
00:35:57,739 --> 00:35:58,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ivan, utrkne ga.

959
00:35:58,599 --> 00:36:00,659
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

960
00:36:00,659 --> 00:36:01,460
[SPEAKER_00] On je učenik

961
00:36:01,460 --> 00:36:02,139
[SPEAKER_00] kojeg je Isus

962
00:36:02,139 --> 00:36:03,239
[SPEAKER_00] osobito ljubio.

963
00:36:03,239 --> 00:36:04,619
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto ga osobito ljubio?

964
00:36:04,619 --> 00:36:05,940
[SPEAKER_00] Zato je li Isus ima miljenike.

965
00:36:05,940 --> 00:36:07,199
[SPEAKER_00] Pa sumlja.

966
00:36:09,019 --> 00:36:10,760
[SPEAKER_00] nego on je bio s njim.

967
00:36:10,760 --> 00:36:13,320
[SPEAKER_00] On je mogao to osjetiti

968
00:36:13,320 --> 00:36:15,360
[SPEAKER_00] jer je on bio uz njega.

969
00:36:15,360 --> 00:36:17,539
[SPEAKER_00] I osluškivao je njegovo srce.

970
00:36:17,539 --> 00:36:18,980
[SPEAKER_00] I sad imamo

971
00:36:18,980 --> 00:36:20,380
[SPEAKER_00] događaj Kalvarije.

972
00:36:20,380 --> 00:36:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ko je ispod Isusova križa?

973
00:36:23,000 --> 00:36:24,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ko je izdržao do kraja?

974
00:36:24,619 --> 00:36:28,539
[SPEAKER_00] Marija i Ivan.

975
00:36:28,539 --> 00:36:30,079
[SPEAKER_00] Marte nema,

976
00:36:30,079 --> 00:36:31,280
[SPEAKER_00] Petar je pobjegao

977
00:36:31,280 --> 00:36:32,480
[SPEAKER_00] u strahu od sluškinje.

978
00:36:32,480 --> 00:36:35,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ako naučimo prebivat

979
00:36:35,099 --> 00:36:37,239
[SPEAKER_00] kraj njega

980
00:36:37,239 --> 00:36:38,179
[SPEAKER_00] i živjeti s njim,

981
00:36:38,280 --> 00:36:38,739
[SPEAKER_00] biti s njim,

982
00:36:38,739 --> 00:36:39,820
[SPEAKER_00] imati odnos s njim

983
00:36:39,820 --> 00:36:40,559
[SPEAKER_00] kao David

984
00:36:40,559 --> 00:36:42,460
[SPEAKER_00] koji je izgubio sve

985
00:36:42,460 --> 00:36:43,179
[SPEAKER_00] više puta

986
00:36:43,179 --> 00:36:44,280
[SPEAKER_00] ali nikad nije izgubio

987
00:36:44,280 --> 00:36:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] odnos s njim

988
00:36:45,000 --> 00:36:46,639
[SPEAKER_00] i razvije cijelu lepezu

989
00:36:46,639 --> 00:36:47,920
[SPEAKER_00] osjećaja prema Bogu

990
00:36:47,920 --> 00:36:49,119
[SPEAKER_00] što čitamo u psalmima,

991
00:36:49,119 --> 00:36:55,780
[SPEAKER_00] onda ćemo izdržati

992
00:36:55,780 --> 00:36:56,800
[SPEAKER_00] i onda kad dođe kušnja.

993
00:36:56,800 --> 00:36:57,360
[SPEAKER_00] I znate šta?

994
00:36:59,099 --> 00:37:00,360
[SPEAKER_00] Ni Marija, Magdalena,

995
00:37:00,360 --> 00:37:02,099
[SPEAKER_00] ni Ivan apostol

996
00:37:02,099 --> 00:37:02,840
[SPEAKER_00] nisu umrli

997
00:37:02,840 --> 00:37:03,920
[SPEAKER_00] mučeničkom smrću.

998
00:37:03,920 --> 00:37:05,400
[SPEAKER_00] Svi apostoli jesu,

999
00:37:05,400 --> 00:37:08,039
[SPEAKER_00] ali njih dvoje nisu.

1000
00:37:08,039 --> 00:37:09,059
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

1001
00:37:09,059 --> 00:37:11,099
[SPEAKER_00] Pa nije bilo potrebno.

1002
00:37:11,099 --> 00:37:12,420
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su već tad bili spremni

1003
00:37:12,420 --> 00:37:13,119
[SPEAKER_00] umret za njega.

1004
00:37:13,119 --> 00:37:14,880
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su došli tamo do kraja.

1005
00:37:14,880 --> 00:37:16,139
[SPEAKER_00] Unatoč rimskoj vojsci,

1006
00:37:16,139 --> 00:37:18,019
[SPEAKER_00] unatoč velikim svećenicima.

1007
00:37:18,579 --> 00:37:18,920
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

1008
00:37:18,920 --> 00:37:20,460
[SPEAKER_00] Zato je li ih je ljubav

1009
00:37:20,460 --> 00:37:21,380
[SPEAKER_00] motivirala.

1010
00:37:21,380 --> 00:37:24,840
[SPEAKER_00] Mi moramo doći od toga

1011
00:37:24,840 --> 00:37:25,800
[SPEAKER_00] da nam ljubav

1012
00:37:25,800 --> 00:37:28,539
[SPEAKER_00] postane motiv našeg djelovanja,

1013
00:37:28,539 --> 00:37:30,980
[SPEAKER_00] a to ne možemo odlučiti,

1014
00:37:30,980 --> 00:37:33,940
[SPEAKER_00] nego to možemo upiti

1015
00:37:33,940 --> 00:37:35,460
[SPEAKER_00] izdruženja s njim,

1016
00:37:35,460 --> 00:37:38,019
[SPEAKER_00] izboravka s njim.

1017
00:37:38,019 --> 00:37:39,679
[SPEAKER_00] E to je dublje predanje.

1018
00:37:39,679 --> 00:37:41,920
[SPEAKER_00] Nije to neka velika filozofija.

1019
00:37:41,920 --> 00:37:43,619
[SPEAKER_00] To je teologija koljena,

1020
00:37:43,619 --> 00:37:46,440
[SPEAKER_00] koja se uči na koljenima pred njim.

1021
00:37:48,579 --> 00:37:53,199
[SPEAKER_00] Završit ću sa

1022
00:37:53,199 --> 00:37:55,800
[SPEAKER_00] jednom objavom

1023
00:37:55,800 --> 00:37:56,780
[SPEAKER_00] koja je jako aktualna,

1024
00:37:56,780 --> 00:37:58,099
[SPEAKER_00] ali riječ o križnom putu,

1025
00:37:58,099 --> 00:37:59,739
[SPEAKER_00] koje Isus dao svoj službenici

1026
00:37:59,739 --> 00:38:01,199
[SPEAKER_00] sveto Jozefi Menendez.

1027
00:38:01,199 --> 00:38:03,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je inače bila ponizna časna sestra

1028
00:38:03,960 --> 00:38:05,340
[SPEAKER_00] koja je

1029
00:38:05,340 --> 00:38:07,960
[SPEAKER_00] ponizna časna sestra

1030
00:38:07,960 --> 00:38:09,800
[SPEAKER_00] koja je cijeli svoj vijek

1031
00:38:09,800 --> 00:38:11,559
[SPEAKER_00] u samostalnu provela u svincu.

1032
00:38:11,559 --> 00:38:13,460
[SPEAKER_00] I niko od njenih sestara

1033
00:38:13,460 --> 00:38:15,400
[SPEAKER_00] nije znao da ona ima mistične objave,

1034
00:38:15,400 --> 00:38:16,699
[SPEAKER_00] osim njenog duhovnika,

1035
00:38:16,699 --> 00:38:18,260
[SPEAKER_00] koji je naredio da to

1036
00:38:18,260 --> 00:38:19,099
[SPEAKER_00] naredio,

1037
00:38:19,099 --> 00:38:20,599
[SPEAKER_00] baš izrečito naredio

1038
00:38:20,599 --> 00:38:22,639
[SPEAKER_00] da pod poslušnost mora to napisat.

1039
00:38:22,639 --> 00:38:25,199
[SPEAKER_00] I nakon smrti je to objavljeno njen.

1040
00:38:25,199 --> 00:38:27,420
[SPEAKER_00] I ona govori

1041
00:38:27,420 --> 00:38:30,059
[SPEAKER_00] baš o ovom čeg smo se dotakli

1042
00:38:30,059 --> 00:38:31,019
[SPEAKER_00] na svetoj misi,

1043
00:38:31,019 --> 00:38:33,840
[SPEAKER_00] vjernicima koji su tu prisutni,

1044
00:38:33,840 --> 00:38:34,559
[SPEAKER_00] koji dolazi.

1045
00:38:35,880 --> 00:38:38,380
[SPEAKER_00] i kroz meditaciju križnog puta

1046
00:38:38,380 --> 00:38:42,300
[SPEAKER_00] ona govori o petoj posta

1047
00:38:42,300 --> 00:38:43,539
[SPEAKER_00] i o Šimunu Cirencu.

1048
00:38:43,539 --> 00:38:46,639
[SPEAKER_00] Takvi smo mnogi.

1049
00:38:46,639 --> 00:38:49,300
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, Šimun je

1050
00:38:49,300 --> 00:38:50,099
[SPEAKER_00] unajmljen.

1051
00:38:50,099 --> 00:38:51,500
[SPEAKER_00] Što znači

1052
00:38:51,500 --> 00:38:53,219
[SPEAKER_00] da se nada nekakvu

1053
00:38:53,219 --> 00:38:55,420
[SPEAKER_00] interesu od rada na koje je prisiljen.

1054
00:38:55,940 --> 00:38:57,159
[SPEAKER_00] Tako i mi često gledamo.

1055
00:38:57,159 --> 00:38:59,500
[SPEAKER_00] Dao sam se Bogu,

1056
00:38:59,500 --> 00:39:00,519
[SPEAKER_00] počeo sam postiti,

1057
00:39:00,519 --> 00:39:00,900
[SPEAKER_00] moliti,

1058
00:39:00,900 --> 00:39:02,360
[SPEAKER_00] sve nešto otišlo gore.

1059
00:39:02,360 --> 00:39:05,019
[SPEAKER_00] Pa nije otišlo gore,

1060
00:39:05,019 --> 00:39:05,940
[SPEAKER_00] nego je tvoje srce,

1061
00:39:05,940 --> 00:39:07,599
[SPEAKER_00] tvoji motivi su sad na kušnji.

1062
00:39:09,179 --> 00:39:10,980
[SPEAKER_00] Bog ne želi da ti budeš unajmljen

1063
00:39:10,980 --> 00:39:12,099
[SPEAKER_00] koji zbog dobitka,

1064
00:39:12,099 --> 00:39:14,980
[SPEAKER_00] nekog jeftinog dobitka

1065
00:39:14,980 --> 00:39:16,739
[SPEAKER_00] koji ćeš i tako jednog dana izgubiti,

1066
00:39:16,739 --> 00:39:17,900
[SPEAKER_00] dolaziš k njemu.

1067
00:39:17,900 --> 00:39:19,519
[SPEAKER_00] On će ti sve to i nadodati,

1068
00:39:19,519 --> 00:39:21,119
[SPEAKER_00] ali nađi njega najprije.

1069
00:39:21,119 --> 00:39:23,019
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže,

1070
00:39:23,019 --> 00:39:24,679
[SPEAKER_00] tako je sa mnogim dušama

1071
00:39:24,679 --> 00:39:25,940
[SPEAKER_00] koji idu za mnom.

1072
00:39:25,940 --> 00:39:30,099
[SPEAKER_00] One nedvojbeno prihvaćaju

1073
00:39:30,099 --> 00:39:32,780
[SPEAKER_00] pomagati mi nositi križ,

1074
00:39:32,780 --> 00:39:36,179
[SPEAKER_00] ali brinu o svoj utjesi i odmoru.

1075
00:39:36,179 --> 00:39:38,239
[SPEAKER_00] Pristaju slijediti me,

1076
00:39:38,239 --> 00:39:40,760
[SPEAKER_00] ali se ne odriču vlastite koristi,

1077
00:39:40,760 --> 00:39:43,739
[SPEAKER_00] koje za njih i dalje na prvom mjestu.

1078
00:39:43,739 --> 00:39:46,900
[SPEAKER_00] Što je tebi na prvom mjestu?

1079
00:39:46,900 --> 00:39:49,480
[SPEAKER_00] O čemu razmišljaš?

1080
00:39:49,480 --> 00:39:51,079
[SPEAKER_00] Kao ovaj svečenik

1081
00:39:51,079 --> 00:39:53,400
[SPEAKER_00] koji je dao mjeru od pola sata.

1082
00:39:53,400 --> 00:39:55,860
[SPEAKER_00] O čemu razmišljaš?

1083
00:39:55,860 --> 00:39:58,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ono o čemu razmišljaš najviše,

1084
00:39:58,840 --> 00:39:59,679
[SPEAKER_00] to je tvoj Bog.

1085
00:40:06,679 --> 00:40:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zato joj kljevaju i puštaju da moj križ padne,

1086
00:40:10,000 --> 00:40:12,579
[SPEAKER_00] kada im njegov teret postane pretežak.

1087
00:40:12,579 --> 00:40:14,300
[SPEAKER_00] Unatoč sirencu križe pada,

1088
00:40:14,300 --> 00:40:15,340
[SPEAKER_00] ali tako, Isusov.

1089
00:40:15,340 --> 00:40:16,159
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže,

1090
00:40:16,260 --> 00:40:18,840
[SPEAKER_00] nastoje trpjeti što je moguće manje,

1091
00:40:18,840 --> 00:40:21,219
[SPEAKER_00] mjere svoje odricanje,

1092
00:40:21,219 --> 00:40:23,320
[SPEAKER_00] izbjegavaju poniženja,

1093
00:40:23,320 --> 00:40:24,500
[SPEAKER_00] umor i rad,

1094
00:40:24,500 --> 00:40:26,639
[SPEAKER_00] pokušavajući sebi preskrbiti,

1095
00:40:26,639 --> 00:40:27,900
[SPEAKER_00] barem neke užitki,

1096
00:40:27,900 --> 00:40:30,900
[SPEAKER_00] prihvaćajući samo ono što ne mogu izbjeći,

1097
00:40:31,539 --> 00:40:33,380
[SPEAKER_00] ili ono na što su strogo obvezni.

1098
00:40:33,380 --> 00:40:35,380
[SPEAKER_00] Nedeljom ću odradit,

1099
00:40:35,380 --> 00:40:36,539
[SPEAKER_00] post,

1100
00:40:36,539 --> 00:40:37,800
[SPEAKER_00] pepelnica,

1101
00:40:37,800 --> 00:40:38,739
[SPEAKER_00] veliki petak,

1102
00:40:38,739 --> 00:40:40,159
[SPEAKER_00] to je to.

1103
00:40:40,159 --> 00:40:42,500
[SPEAKER_00] Na to smo strogo obvezni.

1104
00:40:42,500 --> 00:40:43,699
[SPEAKER_00] Temi duše,

1105
00:40:43,699 --> 00:40:44,559
[SPEAKER_00] kaže Isus,

1106
00:40:44,559 --> 00:40:47,659
[SPEAKER_00] pomažu nositi samo malen dio križa

1107
00:40:47,659 --> 00:40:51,539
[SPEAKER_00] i na taj će način jedva steć zasluge

1108
00:40:51,539 --> 00:40:53,440
[SPEAKER_00] nužne za svoje spasenje.

1109
00:40:53,440 --> 00:40:58,280
[SPEAKER_00] Ali u vječnosti će vidjeti koliko su zaostale na putu.

1110
00:40:58,280 --> 00:41:01,059
[SPEAKER_00] Duša koja istinski ljubi,

1111
00:41:01,059 --> 00:41:03,380
[SPEAKER_00] ne mjeri to što čini,

1112
00:41:03,380 --> 00:41:05,760
[SPEAKER_00] niti važe koliko trpi.

1113
00:41:05,760 --> 00:41:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ona se ne cijenka ni oko rada,

1114
00:41:09,000 --> 00:41:09,780
[SPEAKER_00] ni oko umora.

1115
00:41:09,780 --> 00:41:12,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ona ne očekuje nagradu,

1116
00:41:12,079 --> 00:41:14,019
[SPEAKER_00] nego slijedi sve ono za što misli

1117
00:41:14,019 --> 00:41:16,659
[SPEAKER_00] da će biti najveća slava njezinom Bogu.

1118
00:41:17,659 --> 00:41:21,699
[SPEAKER_00] I zato što dijeluje odano,

1119
00:41:21,699 --> 00:41:23,239
[SPEAKER_00] bez obzira na rezultat,

1120
00:41:23,239 --> 00:41:25,579
[SPEAKER_00] ona se ne pokušava opravdavati,

1121
00:41:25,579 --> 00:41:30,039
[SPEAKER_00] niti mrmljati radi svoje muke nekome.

1122
00:41:30,039 --> 00:41:32,059
[SPEAKER_00] I zato što dijeluje iz ljubavi,

1123
00:41:32,059 --> 00:41:34,360
[SPEAKER_00] njezini će napori i patnje

1124
00:41:34,360 --> 00:41:36,400
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek biti na Božju slavu.

1125
00:41:36,400 --> 00:41:38,480
[SPEAKER_00] Zato se ona ne uznemiruje

1126
00:41:38,480 --> 00:41:40,519
[SPEAKER_00] i ne zabrinjava,

1127
00:41:40,519 --> 00:41:41,619
[SPEAKER_00] a još manje,

1128
00:41:41,619 --> 00:41:44,840
[SPEAKER_00] ako u nekoj prilici najđe na protivštine

1129
00:41:44,840 --> 00:41:46,860
[SPEAKER_00] progon i poniženja,

1130
00:41:46,860 --> 00:41:49,519
[SPEAKER_00] jer jedini pokretač dijelovanja

1131
00:41:49,519 --> 00:41:50,360
[SPEAKER_00] bila je ljubav,

1132
00:41:50,360 --> 00:41:53,199
[SPEAKER_00] a jedini cilj Božja ljubav.

1133
00:41:53,199 --> 00:41:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Te duše nose cijeli teret moga križa

1134
00:41:57,000 --> 00:41:58,480
[SPEAKER_00] bez ikakve koristi

1135
00:41:58,480 --> 00:41:59,840
[SPEAKER_00] i plaće osim ljubavi.

1136
00:41:59,840 --> 00:42:02,440
[SPEAKER_00] Upravo one odmaraju moje srce,

1137
00:42:02,440 --> 00:42:04,239
[SPEAKER_00] upravo ga one prostavljaju.

1138
00:42:04,239 --> 00:42:05,340
[SPEAKER_00] I budite sigurni,

1139
00:42:05,340 --> 00:42:07,219
[SPEAKER_00] ako vaše odricanje

1140
00:42:07,219 --> 00:42:08,659
[SPEAKER_00] i vaše trpljenje

1141
00:42:08,659 --> 00:42:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] dugo ne donese ploda

1142
00:42:10,000 --> 00:42:12,179
[SPEAKER_00] ili se čini da ne donosi nikakav plod,

1143
00:42:12,179 --> 00:42:14,400
[SPEAKER_00] oni nisu bili ni uzaludni

1144
00:42:14,400 --> 00:42:16,059
[SPEAKER_00] ni bezkorisni,

1145
00:42:16,059 --> 00:42:17,900
[SPEAKER_00] jer će jednoga dana

1146
00:42:17,900 --> 00:42:19,400
[SPEAKER_00] žetva biti velika.

1147
00:42:19,400 --> 00:42:22,059
[SPEAKER_00] Ja znam da ovo zvuči

1148
00:42:22,059 --> 00:42:23,199
[SPEAKER_00] kao veliki zahtjev,

1149
00:42:23,199 --> 00:42:24,739
[SPEAKER_00] i meni osobno i svima vama.

1150
00:42:25,739 --> 00:42:28,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ali taj zahtjev se postiže

1151
00:42:28,980 --> 00:42:30,619
[SPEAKER_00] postupno i polako,

1152
00:42:30,619 --> 00:42:33,119
[SPEAKER_00] sa jednom malom odlukom.

1153
00:42:33,119 --> 00:42:34,920
[SPEAKER_00] Kao i kod Jezefe Menendez.

1154
00:42:34,920 --> 00:42:37,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ima posao koji nije dostojanstven.

1155
00:42:37,500 --> 00:42:39,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je sestra, časna,

1156
00:42:39,380 --> 00:42:40,980
[SPEAKER_00] imala svoj poziv

1157
00:42:40,980 --> 00:42:41,920
[SPEAKER_00] da služi Bogu

1158
00:42:41,920 --> 00:42:43,860
[SPEAKER_00] i završila kao zgajatelj svinja.

1159
00:42:43,860 --> 00:42:47,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, malo po malo,

1160
00:42:47,480 --> 00:42:48,840
[SPEAKER_00] malo po malo,

1161
00:42:48,840 --> 00:42:49,960
[SPEAKER_00] malo po malo,

1162
00:42:49,960 --> 00:42:50,980
[SPEAKER_00] velika svetost.

1163
00:42:51,940 --> 00:42:54,480
[SPEAKER_00] Nemojte, kaže Blaženja Lojzija Stepinac,

1164
00:42:54,480 --> 00:42:55,599
[SPEAKER_00] kone napreduje,

1165
00:42:55,599 --> 00:42:56,539
[SPEAKER_00] nazaduje.

1166
00:42:56,539 --> 00:42:58,559
[SPEAKER_00] Idite malim koracima

1167
00:42:58,559 --> 00:42:59,820
[SPEAKER_00] i sigurno

1168
00:42:59,820 --> 00:43:01,840
[SPEAKER_00] prema Božjoj proslavi

1169
00:43:01,840 --> 00:43:03,400
[SPEAKER_00] ovdje i sada.

1170
00:43:03,400 --> 00:43:04,400
[SPEAKER_00] Amen.

